name: cp20231018-BusinessRulesMissingPrefix

metadata.Purpose: Expect Warning: One of the files in the ZIP does not have the correct prefix of BusinessRule_ and the expectation is that the rest of the BRs that do have a proper prefix are imported and the one with a bad prefix is mentioned in the execution report as a warning.
